gw.api.json

Class JsonWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.api.json.JsonWrapper
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    jsonschema.gw.pl.framework.linking.v1_0.Links

    public abstract class JsonWrapper
extends java.lang.Object
    Base class for generated JSON schema wrapper classes. JsonWrappers wrap an underlying JsonObject, with get/set calls on the schema wrapper classes calling through to the underlying JsonObject. As a special case, any getter calls on the generated schema wrapper classes that return a List of nested objects will proxy the underlying JsonObject value to wrap and unwrap as values are retrieved or added.
